{"tid":1399463,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"尚德區剛剛有個阿伯想打人","createTime":"2019-08-03T07:26:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T07:51:26.000Z","uid":173936,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2930ed5be9c0543c7970b944bb56c4f8d588cb86","tid":1399463,"uid":173936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:26:49.000Z","msg":"首先唔該曬啱啱位小妹妹幫手整走張banner<br />\n<br />\n話說喺唐明街同唐俊街嘅十字路口，有個冇議員名嘅banner掛咗喺個轉彎位，所以有個小妹妹過去剪走咗條膠索帶<br />\n結果就有位著粉紅色衫嘅阿伯拎住個黑背囊想去打佢，好彩小妹妹走得切去對面馬路，所以我未出手就已經完咗，但代價係影唔到佢正面<br />\n<br />\n聽日去將軍澳嘅小心啲呢個工聯會票倉"},{"pid":"1463be0be8df6f7b9d3377530d66cb85334b202d","tid":1399463,"uid":173936,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:29:26.000Z","msg":"請原諒我影唔切粉紅色衫嗰位人士嘅正面<br />\n<br />\nBTW上載圖片係咪一定要等咁耐"},{"pid":"1577682cc87c1ee702497a3cb483bd36c427e18e","tid":1399463,"uid":90034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:31:08.000Z","msg":"依啲嘢夜晚冇人先好做呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c64ce7ce987cdc23ca7ab0cc775316eee5d2ac1b","tid":1399463,"uid":173936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:31:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/folderview?id=1-2ZgBVKn9cDgVzF0VYCY4PppbYoxbyzO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffolderview%3Fid%3D1-2ZgBVKn9cDgVzF0VYCY4PppbYoxbyzO&d=MMgAXMBwwZFGDPTkcL6Jsa9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=e215ddfb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/folderview?id=1-2ZgBVKn9cDgVzF0VYCY4PppbYoxbyzO</a><br />\n<br />\n我啱啱影完張完好無缺嘅banner，之後個女仔就出現剪咗<br />\n之後個阿伯就衝出嚟<br />\n<br />\n唔信嘅話可以check返個影相嘅時間"},{"pid":"f674fb9f43581636a22f17cd73b3e73428d1a090","tid":1399463,"uid":173936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c64ce7ce987cdc23ca7ab0cc775316eee5d2ac1b","tid":1399463,"uid":173936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:31:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/folderview?id=